			<![CDATA[<b>A:</b>	Which movie would you rather see at the Cineplex—the new horror film or that hilarious comedy?	
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="Actually, I'd rather rent a movie."/> 
<b>A:</b> 	OK.  What do you want to rent?
<b>B:</b> 	I don’t know.  Definitely not a horror film.  
<b>A:</b> 	What about a comedy?  Maybe a movie with Jim Carrey?
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="I'm sorry, but I can't stand him!"/> 
<b>A:</b> 	Really?  I love him!
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="How about a romantic movie?"/>  
<b>A:</b> 	Great idea.  I'm in the mood for a love story!
<b>B:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="I hear {i}Last Love{/i} is good."/>
<b>A:</b>	&nbsp;<blank word="{i}Last Love{/i}? Now you're talking!"/>]]>
		</text>

